title: Sarah Lacina Reflects on Her ‘Challenge: USA’ Win | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Johnny is joined by Sarah Lacina, winner of ‘The Challenge: USA,’ to discuss the controversy surrounding the final, her beef with Tyson Apostol, and what makes her a great ‘Challenge’ competitor.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Sarah Lacina
Producer: Sasha Ashall
